22 'บ    This is another program showing the techniques for programming a     บ
24 'บ series of screen boxes.  You may use any of the subroutines alone to    บ
25 'บ place a box anywhere on the screen. Note that INITIALIZATION statement  บ
26 'บ establishes the four corner coordinates for the box.  You can easily    บ
28 'บ put a box where you wish by the simple and FAST insertion of only four  บ
30 'บ numbers.  The technique for programming the SOFT keys for a particular  บ
32 'บ qualified response is also demonstrated.  This uses the INKEY$ function บ
34 'บ to to examine the character returned.  All other returns (except that   บ
